The paper focuses on hyper-parameter tuning for deep learning algorithms, which is a common topic in machine learning and artificial intelligence research. Therefore, cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) are the most likely categories. The paper also specifically mentions two types of deep neural networks, Recurrent Neural Networks and Convolutional Neural Networks, which are commonly used in computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL) tasks. Additionally, the paper mentions the use of Bayesian Optimization, which is a common optimization technique in neural network research (cs.NE).
